field_5dd69f343e423'),(7606,1584,'cta_content','Call For a Free Quote today<br/>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 442 4500 - <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 490 1936'),(7607,1584,'_cta_content','field_5dd69f413e424'),(7608,1584,'cta_button_text','Contact Us en'),(7609,1584,'_cta_button_text','field_5dd69f503e425'),(7610,1584,'cta_button_link','http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/contact-us/'),(7611,1584,'_cta_button_link','field_5dd69f643e426'),(7612,1584,'section_title','Restorations And Repair Service en'),(7613,1584,'_section_title','field_5dd6a0051c093'),(7614,1584,'section_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Re-fringe:</strong> The fringe is hand sewn and there are many different type to choose from, so it looks original and matching. en</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Binding:</strong> it stops the rug from unraveling and fraying.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Overcasting:</strong> The side finish on rugs may detach from the rug, wear down from traffic, get chewed off by pets.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Serging:</strong> for finish off certain type of rugs the yarn is serge around the border which gives the rug a finished look and stops from unraveling.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Lock-stitching:</strong> Stops rugs from unraveling which can cause major damages and lower the value of antique rugs. A neatly, and nearly invisible stitch is sewn back and forth from end to end. Appraisals. Trade Ins, welcome.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(7615,1584,'_section_content','field_5dd6a0261c094'),(7616,1584,'video_background_image','141'),(7617,1584,'_video_background_image','field_5dd6a0311c095'),(7618,1584,'youtube_video_link','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LjJyKNAQwNI'),(7619,1584,'_youtube_video_link','field_5dd6a0411c096'),(7620,1036,'_yst_prominent_words_version','1'),(7621,1036,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(7622,1036,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskeywords','[]'),(7623,1036,'_yoast_wpseo_keywordsynonyms','[\"\"]'),(7624,1585,'cleaning_process_steps','<h5><strong>El proceso de limpieza para alfombras orientales es un proceso de varios pasos que incluye.</strong></h5>\r\n<ol class=\"order_list\">\r\n 	<li>Inspección de prelavado para determinar la calidad y el estado general de la alfombra.</li>\r\n 	<li>Prueba de tinte, para determinar la solidez del color.</li>\r\n 	<li>Polvo de poder, para sacar la tierra suelta.</li>\r\n 	<li>Pretratamiento para la eliminación deportiva.</li>\r\n 	<li>Limpieza y enjuague de manos.</li>\r\n 	<li>Eliminación de humedad con escurridor.</li>\r\n 	<li>Secado en un ambiente con humedad controlada.</li>\r\n 	<li>Utilizamos tratamientos antimicrobianos, enzimas, para eliminar olores fuertes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Descontaminación de orina: la opción agresiva cuando una alfombra tiene manchas y olor excesivos. El proceso incluye desinfectar, desodorizar y desinfectar.</li>\r\n</ol>'),(7625,1585,'_cleaning_process_steps','field_5e00e4e530e46'),(7626,1585,'cta_title','Pick Up And Delivery Service Available. es'),(7627,1585,'_cta_title','field_5e017b1b39a69'),(7628,1585,'cta_content','Call For a Free Quote today<br/>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 442 4500 - <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 490 1936'),(7629,1585,'_cta_content','field_5e017b1b39e37'),(7630,1585,'cta_button_text','Contact Us es'),(7631,1585,'_cta_button_text','field_5e017b1b3a228'),(7632,1585,'cta_button_link','http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/contact-us/'),(7633,1585,'_cta_button_link','field_5e017b1b3a62e'),(7634,1585,'section_title','Servicio de Restauraciones y Reparaciones'),(7635,1585,'_section_title','field_5e018219706c9'),(7636,1585,'section_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Re-flecos:</strong> el fleco está cosido a mano y hay muchos tipos diferentes para elegir, por lo que se ve original y combina.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Encuadernación:</strong> evita que la alfombra se deshilache y se deshilache.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Revestimiento:</strong> el acabado lateral de las alfombras puede desprenderse de la alfombra, desgastarse por el tráfico y ser masticado por las mascotas.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Serging:</strong> para rematar cierto tipo de alfombras, el hilo se enrolla alrededor del borde, lo que le da a la alfombra un aspecto acabado y evita que se desenrede.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Costuras de bloqueo:</strong> evita que las alfombras se desenreden, lo que puede causar daños importantes y disminuir el valor de las alfombras antiguas. Se cose una puntada prolija y casi invisible de un extremo a otro. Tasaciones Trade Ins, bienvenido.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(7637,1585,'_section_content','field_5e01821970ae3'),(7638,1585,'video_background_image','141'),(7639,1585,'_video_background_image','field_5e01821970e77'),(7640,1585,'youtube_video_link','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LjJyKNAQwNI'),(7641,1585,'_youtube_video_link','field_5e01821971239'),(7642,1586,'cleaning_process_steps','<h5><strong>The Cleaning Process For Oriental Rugs Is A Multi-Step Process Which Includes:\r\n</strong></h5>\r\n<ol class=\"order_list\">\r\n 	<li>Pre-wash inspection to determine Rug quality and overall condition.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dye testing, to determine the color fastness.</li>\r\n 	<li>Power dusting, to get out the loose soil.</li>\r\n 	<li>Pre-treatment for sport removal.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hand cleaning and Rinsing.</li>\r\n 	<li>Moisture removal with wringer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Drying in a humidity-controlled environment.</li>\r\n 	<li>We use Anti-microbial treatments, enzymes, for removal of strong odor.</li>\r\n 	<li>Urine decontamination: the aggressive option when a rug has excessive staining and odor. the process includes disinfect-deodorize and sanitize.</li>\r\n</ol>'),(7643,1586,'_cleaning_process_steps','field_5dd69e837dd0e'),(7644,1586,'cta_title','Pick Up And Delivery Service Available. en'),(7645,1586,'_cta_title','field_5dd69f343e423'),(7646,1586,'cta_content','Call For a Free Quote today<br/>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 442 4500 - <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> 305 490 1936'),(7647,1586,'_cta_content','field_5d