red, the Process includes brushing the Rug and the fringes is very important component of the Rug, because it\'s the extension of the warp threads, that makes the foundation of the Rug.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Carpet Cleaning/Repair','','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2019-12-28 18:00:54','2019-12-28 18:00:54','',22,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1587,1,'2019-11-12 02:39:34','2019-11-12 02:39:34','','banner1','','inherit','open','closed','','banner1-2','','','2019-12-28 21:25:17','2019-12-28 21:25:17','',1174,'http://localhost/GrandOrientalRugGalleryWordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/banner1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1588,1,'2019-11-12 02:39:34','2019-11-12 02:39:34','','banner1','','inherit','open','closed','','banner1-2','','','2019-12-28 21:25:25','2019-12-28 21:25:25','',37,'http://localhost/GrandOrientalRugGalleryWordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/banner1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1589,1,'2019-12-28 21:39:42','2019-12-28 21:39:42','','cowhide-animal-print','','inherit','open','closed','','cowhide-animal-print','','','2019-12-28 21:39:59','2019-12-28 21:39:59','',0,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cowhide-animal-print.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1590,1,'2019-12-28 21:39:42','2019-12-28 21:39:42','','piel de vaca animal print','','inherit','open','closed','','cowhide-animal-print','','','2019-12-28 21:42:21','2019-12-28 21:42:21','',0,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cowhide-animal-print.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1592,1,'2019-12-29 13:47:49','2019-12-29 13:47:49','{\n    \"ubermenu_main[style_top_level_background_hover]\": {\n        \"value\": \"#ffffff,#ffffff\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-12-29 13:47:45\"\n    },\n    \"ubermenu_main[style_top_level_backgrou